Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.74,0:00:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama}! {*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama}!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.08,0:00:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo, boy. That looks like bad news.{lit: "we should hurry up and get out of here or else things will get bad". first bit is kinda not expressed here. Maybe add "We should probably head out."?}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.79,0:00:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe they chased us all the way out here.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.08,0:00:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.04,0:00:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They just opened fire in {\i1}our{\i0} school district!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.84,0:00:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Were they aiming at us, or were they \Ntrying to take out Problem Solver 68?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.47,0:00:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Teacher{*Sensei}, are they who I think they are?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.01,0:00:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.47,0:00:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They're...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.85,0:00:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the Gehenna Prefect Team.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.28,0:02:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Teacher{*Sensei}, it's dangerous here.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.37,0:02:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Get clear and keep your head down.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.49,0:02:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.41,0:02:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,God, what a pain.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.08,0:02:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Put up with it, Iori. {This phrase has been ruined by the sunglasses meme. Also Chinatsu talks a bit like your mum would, so I don't think she'd be quite this blunt about it. --ik}{### how's this?}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.79,0:02:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't we just go in already?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.46,0:02:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Negotiations come first.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.88,0:02:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here to round up some rebellious students \Nfrom our school, not chat over coffee.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.88,0:02:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If they wanna interfere, they can st{uff it}—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.68,0:02:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,First, we explain our intentions.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.18,0:02:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we listen to their side \Nand try to reach a mutual understanding.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.27,0:02:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Only once negotiations fail do we resort to force.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.31,0:02:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why bother with all the red tape?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.23,0:02:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They're from another school.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.94,0:02:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It may have been accidental,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.53,0:02:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but under normal circumstances, attacking another \Nschool's students is a grave offence.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.40,0:02:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay. I get it.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.16,0:02:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go tell them and get this over with, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.95,0:02:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Iori, wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.87,0:03:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax. I got this.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.54,0:03:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wakey wakey, Aru{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.38,0:03:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama}!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.63,0:03:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, {*}sunshine{*Aru-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.09,0:03:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, we need to hurry and get out of here.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.93,0:03:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.51,0:03:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.26,0:03:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Prefect Team's come for us.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.52,0:03:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The Prefect...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.85,0:03:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.02,0:03:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.44,0:03:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Or else they'll hear us.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.81,0:03:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Still no response from Hoshino{**-senpai}?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.03,0:03:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She's never gone dark for this long before.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.45,0:03:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello there, students from Abydos High School.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.33,0:03:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What business does Gehenna's Prefect Team have here?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.83,0:03:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And why did you shell us?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.21,0:03:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We figured we'd mete out some punishment \Nto the gang of rule breakers hiding in this district. {###}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.46,0:03:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about Problem Solver 68?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.30,0:03:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Right on.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.01,0:04:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cut to the chase. We have no business with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.14,0:04:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll let you off with a warning.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.89,0:04:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I suggest you count your blessings and leave.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.73,0:04:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we don't?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.69,0:04:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Prefect Team we're dealing with.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.90,0:04:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're not careful, we could end up seriously hurt.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.94,0:04:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This may even spark a larger political conflict.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.82,0:04:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate that they're allowed to get away with this,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.37,0:04:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but we don't stand a chance against them.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.37,0:04:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we have to obey.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.83,0:04:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not an option.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.92,0:04:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right! We still gotta teach \Nthose Problem Solver clowns a lesson!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.50,0:04:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.50,0:04:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The boss had nothing to do with this, \Nand look at what they did to him!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.92,0:04:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Serika{**-chan}...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.97,0:04:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not leaving.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.43,0:04:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They refused a demand from the Prefects?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.98,0:04:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding. They're {\i1}so{\i0} screwed.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.44,0:04:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama}, now's our chance.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.73,0:04:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We should leave while we can.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.86,0:04:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama}?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.11,0:05:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A true outlaw wouldn't spend her days \Nregretting her past actions, would she?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.53,0:05:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She wouldn't pin her mistakes \Non someone else and slink off like a coward.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.58,0:05:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous. This isn't the time for—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.75,0:05:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A true outlaw...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.92,0:05:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The outlaws we're striving to become
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.67,0:05:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,would never betray their ideals, \Nno matter the enemy. Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.76,0:05:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Aru...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.51,0:05:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So you chose to be difficult.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.81,0:05:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,After I went to the effort of playing nice, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.94,0:05:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say I didn't warn you!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.06,0:05:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayane{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.82,0:05:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Iori?! For the love of—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.17,0:05:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice try.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.89,0:06:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you little!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.73,0:06:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Serika{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.65,0:06:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You call that a fight?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.65,0:06:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.74,0:06:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.33,0:06:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Iori, stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.00,0:06:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here, {*}Teacher{*Sensei}!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.00,0:06:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Teacher{*Sensei}?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.37,0:06:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, are you that teacher from SCHALE?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.67,0:06:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wide open.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.80,0:06:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.34,0:06:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.55,0:06:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I recognised you, {*}Teacher{*Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.18,0:06:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect us to meet again \Nunder these circumstances.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.14,0:06:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.64,0:06:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Chinatsu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.06,0:06:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If only we knew you were here earlier.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.90,0:06:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no excuses.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.94,0:07:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Okusora Ayane from \Nthe Abydos Foreclosure Task Force.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.40,0:07:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand you're with the Gehenna Prefect Team,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.07,0:07:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but could you please explain yourselves?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.66,0:07:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.95,0:07:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to address your concerns.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.00,0:07:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Greetings, Abydos students.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.67,0:07:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the Senior Administrator \Nof Gehenna Academy's Prefect Team.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.55,0:07:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Amau Ako.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.38,0:07:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to take a moment \Nto address what's currently going on. {###}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.39,0:07:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to apologise for the way you were treated.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.35,0:07:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Your apology would be a lot more convincing \Nif you weren't holding us at gunpoint.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.98,0:07:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, where are my manners?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.57,0:07:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All hands, stand down.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.94,0:07:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They seriously lowered their weapons?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.99,0:07:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,As I was saying, I apologise on behalf \Nof my colleague's foolish behaviour.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.16,0:07:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Foolish behaviour?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.49,0:07:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was following your orders! { "I was just following orders" has heavy connotations of "it's not my fault I did something bad", but here she's more like "this was literally part of the plan, what are you talking about" --ik}{### I think in a vacuum that's a fair issue to bring up, but she's being defensive here now and her argument is getting torn apart in front of everyone, so I think it's fine. Did a minor edit, tho}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.21,0:08:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Iori, you remember where the \Napology templates are kept, don't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.54,0:08:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Ako{**-chan}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.88,0:08:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Were your orders to blindly engage by \Nfiring indiscriminately at innocent bystanders?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.64,0:08:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That wasn't... I mean...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.43,0:08:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not in Gehenna. I expect more discretion from you \Nwhen you're acting in another school's district.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.18,0:08:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you know better \Nthan to cause trouble for others?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.36,0:08:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I will ask again, Iori.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.77,0:08:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember where the \Napology templates are kept, don't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.15,0:08:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside your desk, left drawer.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.95,0:08:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect. I trust you know what to do, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.20,0:08:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, back to the main question.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.54,0:08:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The Prefect Team was mobilised to take a group \Nof unruly students into our custody.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.50,0:08:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask for your cooperation in aiding us\Nwith our duties as the Prefect Team.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.67,0:08:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a request, or...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.34,0:08:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's a request.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.72,0:08:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,For now.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.89,0:08:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't do that.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.64,0:08:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? And why not?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.48,0:08:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes without saying.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.39,0:09:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You opened fire in {\i1}our{\i0} district!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.48,0:09:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You did so without following proper procedure{/protocol}. \NThat's a blatant breach of jurisdiction! {"jurisdictional duty" is not idiomatic, afaik. maybe just "breach of jurisdiction". First sentence feels unnatural. Is there a proper procedure for opening fire in someone else's school district, then? Could just cut it entirely to save CPS. --ik}{### want petzku's opinions on what to do with the first half, since I can't think of much I like. I want to give a lot more weight to the second half of the line with the first one, so they have to somehow connect.}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.78,0:09:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll decide how to deal with Problem Solver 68.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.95,0:09:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the teacher from SCHALE share their view?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.74,0:09:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.66,0:09:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering the current situation, \NI stand by their decision.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.92,0:09:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I was hoping for a peaceful resolution.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.04,0:09:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.05,0:09:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All hands, prepare to engage!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.01,0:09:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.64,0:09:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,An ambush?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.68,0:09:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep calm!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.60,0:09:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Check your surroundings!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.27,0:09:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you do that to {*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama}?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.27,0:09:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Unacceptable.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.69,0:09:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Unacceptable. Unacceptable!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.07,0:09:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Iori!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.33,0:09:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Heya! Did you miss me?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.66,0:10:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That went well.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.04,0:10:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.33,0:10:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then. Let's get this show on the road.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.42,0:10:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You! You'll pay for what you did to—
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.75,0:10:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.67,0:10:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.92,0:10:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you chose to show yourselves.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.26,0:10:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But I suppose this saves us \Nthe trouble of searching for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.06,0:10:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They had a reserve force in the back.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.48,0:10:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well. Figured this wasn't gonna be {\i1}that{\i0} easy.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.69,0:10:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I must say, this is quite the happy coincidence.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.90,0:10:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knew chasing Problem Solver 68 \Nwould lead to the teacher from SCHALE?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.07,0:10:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut the act, Ako.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.03,0:10:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.58,0:10:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Kayoko?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.87,0:10:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,QC,A "happy coincidence" my foot.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.62,0:10:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,QC,You were planning this from the start.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.38,0:10:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,QC,All these troops, just for some petty criminals? \NThe Head Prefect would never have authorised this.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.80,0:10:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,QC,{\i1}You{\i0} were anticipating this to escalate \Ninto a full-blown war with Abydos. {TLC: She never mentions here that a "war" was intentional. The idea was more "this is too much firepower for taking on a tiny school like Abydos, so clearly you have other plans here". Honestly, the prior line covers pretty much everything, so deleting this bit and moving some stuff around might solve the problem, if risk not adding in context to a scene that doesn't have that much to begin with --ik} {### This is information not strictly present in the anime, but it is in the game. Without it, this entire speech simply does not connect to the situation, and it doesn't really make sense without it either. Your call, petz.}{I...would say drop this line because it just isn't said *at all* and afaict is forcefully added context (JP viewers who haven't played the game wouldn't get this implication at the very least), and spill over the previous line into this one. the "so much firepower against Abydos" bit is kind of already taken care of more explicitly with the second line after this.}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.55,0:10:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,QC,Your true objective is SCHALE.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.72,0:11:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,QC,This teacher is the reason you deployed \Nan entire army in Abydos.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.43,0:11:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm{\i0} the reason?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.52,0:11:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.56,0:11:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed, Kayoko{**-san}. You're quite observant.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.11,0:11:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. I'm feeling generous today, \Nso I'll explain everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.69,0:11:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It all started with the Tea Party.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.32,0:11:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,As you may know, Trinity has a long-standing \Nhistory of rivalry with Gehenna.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.83,0:11:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Our intelligence division learned of a dossier on SCHALE \Nthat was submitted to their student council.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.75,0:11:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So when the report was brought to my desk, \NI simply couldn't ignore it.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.88,0:11:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea what SCHALE even was at the time,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.67,0:11:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but if the Tea Party had intel on them, \Nit was vital that we acquired it too.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.93,0:11:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So I decided to read the report Chinatsu{**-san} \Nhad prepared on the SCHALE HQ incident.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.06,0:11:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Which I submitted months ago, may I add.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.60,0:11:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A mysterious organisation left behind \Nby the General Student Council President,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.41,0:11:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,headed by the adult over there.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.36,0:11:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no telling how this might \Ntip the scales going forward.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.40,0:11:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we, the Gehenna Prefect Team,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.53,0:12:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,would like to take him into our custody, \Nat least until the Eden Treaty has been safely signed.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.79,0:12:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit dreaming.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.66,0:12:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really think we'd just hand him over?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.25,0:12:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll protect our teacher.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.84,0:12:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I was afraid this would happen.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.97,0:12:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You've left us little choice but to resort to force.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.68,0:12:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Head Prefect finds out about this, \NI'll be writing apologies along with Iori.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.64,0:12:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ako{**-chan}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.06,0:12:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think the five of you can win?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.73,0:12:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's nine of us.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.98,0:12:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.31,0:12:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're not after you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.19,0:12:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a lousy villain would flee \Nwithout settling a debt.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.32,0:12:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our boss!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.95,0:12:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not letting those prefects walk away \Nuntil I've put a bullet through each of their smug faces.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.83,0:12:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ditto.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.62,0:12:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuromi Serika.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.00,0:12:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on the same team for now, \Nso at least get my name right.{"for now" isn't really said, but I guess it technically is still true}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.26,0:12:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not "part-timer".
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.88,0:13:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The name's Rikuhachima Aru.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.39,0:13:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Onikata Kayoko.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.97,0:13:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm Asagi Mutsuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.64,0:13:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm Igusa Haruka.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.64,0:13:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Pleasure to work with you!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.56,0:13:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Izayoi Nonomi.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.52,0:13:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And my name is Okusora Ayane.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.90,0:13:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunaookami Shiroko.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.40,0:13:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.45,0:13:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We're giving you one last chance to surrender.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.57,0:13:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you continue, so be it! You can cry, you can beg, \Nyou can lick my feet all you like, but... {"so be it" is incorrect in context. Maybe "This is your last chance to surrender" for the previous line, then here "I'm serious! ..." Also "all you like" kind of ruins the tempo for me, maybe just nix that and cut it off at feet so that Sensei's response is more clearly at the feet bit.}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.68,0:13:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to, but I'll have to pass this time. {### alt: "I'd love to take you up on that, but maybe some other time."}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.75,0:13:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite the unexpected alliance.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.05,0:13:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But no matter.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.59,0:13:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll soon learn what it means to defy the G—
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.43,0:13:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You talk too much.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.31,0:13:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Commence the operation!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.48,0:13:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonomi, Haruka! Take three o'clock!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.61,0:13:56.36,Default,,0,1100,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.61,0:13:56.36,Default,,1300,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.69,0:13:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Serika, Mutsuki! You two take nine o'clock!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.49,0:14:00.61,Default,,1050,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.49,0:14:00.61,Default,,0,1200,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.86,0:14:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko, Aru! You're up front, high noon!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.53,0:14:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.62,0:14:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayane and Kayoko, support the others.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.66,0:14:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.66,0:14:08.49,Alt,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.75,0:14:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka{**-san}, what should we do?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.62,0:14:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go first.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.58,0:14:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, hold on!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.46,0:14:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, please. Die, please!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.79,0:14:18.46,Alt,,0,0,0,,Haruka{**-san}!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.55,0:14:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Th-Thank you...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.68,0:14:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. Don't mention it!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.85,0:14:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Heads up, part-timer!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.40,0:14:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're not half bad, part-timer!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.53,0:14:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I'm not.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.99,0:14:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's keep the party going!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.62,0:14:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Another grenade incoming!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.08,0:14:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.91,0:14:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, cr—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.92,0:15:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, you filthy rats.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.21,0:15:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.60,0:15:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Great work, Haruka{**-san}!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.35,0:15:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.64,0:15:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all because of you, Nonomi{**-san}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.94,0:15:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, you did great!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.37,0:15:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop your gun and surrender, please.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.79,0:15:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit running around, you cowards!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.92,0:15:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out and face me head-on!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.80,0:15:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She's fast!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.34,0:15:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got you now!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.10,0:15:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She's all yours, part-timer.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.31,0:15:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.89,0:15:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, that's not my name!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.53,0:16:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what do we have here?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.58,0:16:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got some guts, calling me a rat.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.29,0:16:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit. You think you're so tough.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.00,0:16:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kick your asses!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.17,0:16:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for? Get over here!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.05,0:16:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Three o'clock, nine o'clock, all clear. No hostile presence.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.59,0:16:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. All that's left is twelve o'clock.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.26,0:16:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko, Aru. Just a little bit more!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.81,0:16:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, we were interrupted before, but I wonder.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.18,0:16:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If we did end up fighting, \Nwho do you think would win?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.48,0:16:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.32,0:16:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. It is.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.53,0:16:49.40,Default,,1300,0,0,,{\i1}We{\i0} would win. {"Nah I'd win" energy --ML}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.53,0:16:49.40,Default,,0,1300,0,,{\i1}We{\i0} would win.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.66,0:16:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.42,0:17:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.67,0:17:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.55,0:17:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to close the distance, \Nor we'll be sitting ducks!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.18,0:17:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have joined forces,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.35,0:17:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're still powerless against the might of—
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.25,0:17:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we get her?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.51,0:17:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.06,0:18:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like politely asking you to hand over \Nthe teacher is no longer an option.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.49,0:18:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed you can still talk big at this point.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.70,0:18:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up already.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.78,0:18:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you understand the situation.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.75,0:18:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}are{\i0} going to crack eventually.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.37,0:18:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have many soldiers waiting for my command to—
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.63,0:18:26.13,Alt,,0,0,0,,Ako.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.13,0:18:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.13,0:18:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,President Hina?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.09,0:18:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better have a good explanation for this, Ako.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.26,0:18:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I, well, you see...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.35,0:18:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I mobilised the troops to arrest a group \Nof troublemakers, and...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.22,0:18:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Problem Solver 68?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.85,0:18:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are they then?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.10,0:18:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What do you mean? They should be right...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.48,0:18:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.90,0:18:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What? How? They were right there!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.53,0:18:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,President Hina! I can explain this!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.32,0:18:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's all right. I've got the general picture.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.70,0:19:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ako, we're the Prefect Team. \NNot the student council.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.66,0:19:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I, well, I mean...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.04,0:19:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll discuss the details once I'm back.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.21,0:19:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me in the school building until then.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.96,0:19:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.34,0:19:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.55,0:19:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Prefect President, do you understand the situation?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.97,0:19:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There has been an unauthorised military operation \Nwithin another school's district without prior notification,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.31,0:19:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,resulting in a clash with said school's students.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.31,0:19:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. In other words—
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.81,0:19:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it's also true that you obstructed \Nthe duties of the Prefect Team.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.82,0:19:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.24,0:19:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Things have taken quite a turn while I was out, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.91,0:19:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino{**-senpai}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.16,0:19:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What took you so long?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.04,0:19:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that. I was taking a little nap.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.54,0:19:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A nap?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.54,0:19:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hoshino? From Abydos?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.88,0:19:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could this be Takanashi Hoshino?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.30,0:20:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno what's going on here,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.76,0:20:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but what's with the army,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.81,0:20:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Prefect President{*Prefect President-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.02,0:20:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You've changed a lot since your first year.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.90,0:20:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost didn't recognise you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.57,0:20:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Do we know each other?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.07,0:20:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,While I was in the intelligence division,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.57,0:20:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I took note of any students of interest \Nin every school district.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.58,0:20:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying a fellow like me is famous?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.83,0:20:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Takanashi Hoshino.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.70,0:20:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never forget you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.37,0:20:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you had left Abydos following the incident.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.79,0:20:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.96,0:20:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why SCHALE...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.13,0:20:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that now?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.22,0:20:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have something you wanna say, \Nyou'll have to speak a bit more clearly than that.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.31,0:20:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to withdraw.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.27,0:20:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We're leaving?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.40,0:20:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,P-President Hina?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.77,0:20:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Sorasaki Hina, officially apologise \Nto the Abydos Foreclosure Task Force.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.53,0:21:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,On behalf of the Gehenna Prefect Team, \NI apologise for the unauthorised military operation,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.21,0:21:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and for the trouble we caused \Nin another school's territory.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.85,0:21:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask for your foregiveness and understanding.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.29,0:21:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done here.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.87,0:21:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.40,0:21:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Teacher{*Sensei}, what did she say?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.86,0:21:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.61,0:21:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The abandoned desert in Abydos.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.19,0:21:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(3945,4195,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}Kaiser Corporation is plotting something there.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.45,0:21:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Teacher{*Sensei}?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.70,0:21:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo, boy.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.08,0:21:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta say, I'm feeling kinda lost here.
